CreatePluginsFromGenericTypeBenchmarks.description: Benchmarks comparing GeneratedPluginFactory vs ReflectionPluginFactory for creating plugins from a type parameter. Uses REAL generated TypeRegistry from source generator. Reflection is the baseline.

DecoratorResolutionBenchmarks.description: Benchmarks comparing decorated service resolution between source-gen and reflection. All benchmarks measure resolution of a service with a 5-decorator chain. Reflection is the baseline.

HostBuildBenchmarks.description: Benchmarks comparing host build with source-gen vs reflection DI. Measures full host building time including service registration. Reflection is the baseline.

KeyedServiceResolutionBenchmarks.description: Benchmarks comparing keyed service resolution between source-gen and reflection. All benchmarks measure resolution of a keyed service. Reflection is the baseline.

OptionsResolutionBenchmarks.description: Benchmarks comparing IOptions resolution between source-gen and reflection. All benchmarks measure resolution of a single options type. Reflection is the baseline.

ServiceProviderBuildBenchmarks.description: End-to-end benchmarks comparing full Syringe pipeline for source-gen vs reflection. Uses REAL generated TypeRegistry from source generator. Reflection is the baseline.

ServiceResolutionBenchmarks.description: Benchmarks comparing simple service resolution between source-gen and reflection. All benchmarks measure resolution of a simple service (no dependencies). Reflection is the baseline.

TypeRegistrationBenchmarks.description: Benchmarks comparing GeneratedTypeRegistrar vs ReflectionTypeRegistrar. Uses REAL generated TypeRegistry from source generator. Reflection is the baseline.

WebApplicationBuildBenchmarks.description: Benchmarks comparing ASP.NET WebApplication build with source-gen vs reflection DI. Measures full WebApplication building time including service registration. Reflection is the baseline.
